notification.contentToBeAnonymized: Umxholo wakho uza kufihlwa ngokungaziwa emva kweentsuku ezi-7 ngenxa
notification.communityContentToBeAnonymized: Yonke imixholo yakho kule ntlangano iza kufihlwa ngokungaziwa kwaye igcinwe kwi-archive emva kweentsuku ezi-7, emva koko awuyi kuba nakho ukuyicima okanye uyitshintshe. Jonga umxholo wakho ngezantsi.
notification.groupContentToBeAnonymized: Yonke imixholo yakho kuleli qela iza kufihlwa ngokungaziwa kwaye igcinwe kwi-archive emva kweentsuku ezi-7, emva koko awuyi kuba nakho ukuyicima okanye uyitshintshe. Jonga umxholo wakho ngezantsi.

email.possibleFraudFooter: Cofa kwi-link yoluntu ngezantsi, ungene njengomlawuli kwaye ukhethe Ulawulo lweFraud kumenyu.
email.possibleFraudSubHeader: Inani lemisebenzi enokuba yinkohliso enethuba eliqikelelweyo lama-75% lenkohliso
email.possibleFraudInformation: Inkqubo yethu ezenzekelayo ichonge umsebenzi onokuba yinkohliso. Ungajonga ngokusondeleyo nge-Community admin interface. Eminye yale misebenzi inokuba nezizathu ezingeyo inkohliso ke qiniseka ukuba uphanda ngokucokisekileyo ngaphambi kokucima umxholo.
email.automaticToxicityDetection: Umxholo lo ufunyenwe ngokuzenzekelayo njengotyhefayo usebenzisa iialgorithms ze-AI ezilinganisela ubutyhefu bomxholo. Ungawucima umxholo ukuba kuyimfuneko.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionVision: I-algorithm ye-AI ngokuzenzekelayo iflagile imifanekiso eqhagamshelwe kulo mxholo. Le algorithm ihlola imifanekiso ngokubhekiselele kumxholo omdala, onodlame, wezonyango, kunye nemifanekiso engamanyala. Ungawucima umxholo ukuba kuyimfuneko.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionDisclaimer: Ngamanye amaxesha i-algorithm ye-AI ibala amanqaku angalunganga, kule meko musa ukukhathazeka, akufuneki uthathe nanye enye inyathelo kwaye ungayihoya le imeyile.
email.user_invite_2: Cofa kwi-link okanye uyincamathisele kwi-bar yedilesi yesikhangeli ukwamkela isimemo
email.reset_password_2: Ukuba awuzange ucele oku, nceda ungayihoyi le imeyile.
email.reset_password_3: Iphasiwedi yakho ayizukutshintsha de ube ungena kule khonkco ingentla kwaye wenze entsha.
